text:
What...? Keep it short, I'm exhausted from
having to keep that person company.

Why are you playing a character
when you interact with Asahi?

Are you an idiot...? Why should Fuyu have to show 
her real self to somthing like that?

Why...
Because you're part of the same unit, of course.

Ha, can you cut that out already? There's no way
Fuyu's going to get all friendly with that girl.

it'll be troublesome if you continue to get it wrong:
This Fuyu is the normal Fuyu.

You said something about making up a character,
but that character is Fuyu.

That you saw that during that course of events...
That was Fuyu's blunder.

I don't want to show anyone that a Fuyu like that,
and I didn't plan for it to be seen by anyone either.
...don't bring up this tasteless topic anymore.
